.090628,0.086643,0.08569,0.082313,0.076615]},{"section":10,"text":"I remember that when people have excessive anxiety about their health, especially with specific symptoms, it can sometimes be a sign of a somatoform disorder.","dimension":11,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.05557,0.082354,0.085999,0.091083,0.088475,0.088251,0.09157,0.088797,0.087758,0.090564,0.080958,0.068621],"unified_progress":[0.047586,0.072249,0.083859,0.093374,0.093663,0.095035,0.096097,0.09456,0.090458,0.092008,0.078338,0.062773]},{"section":11,"text":"Somatoform disorders are psychological conditions where physical symptoms are experienced in the absence of a clear medical cause.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036414,0.059199,0.074021,0.082895,0.093675,0.099371,0.10265,0.10479,0.10274,0.094251,0.080866,0.069131],"unified_progress":[0.034336,0.059409,0.080147,0.089863,0.097249,0.1054,0.10336,0.10197,0.097227,0.093536,0.077077,0.060427]},{"section":12,"text":"These disorders often involve high levels of anxiety and a belief that the symptoms are indicative of a serious illness.","dimension":2,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.039172,0.058274,0.070466,0.079162,0.08955,0.096507,0.10129,0.10481,0.10392,0.096324,0.084517,0.076007],"unified_progress":[0.039102,0.059903,0.076166,0.087317,0.093704,0.10258,0.10161,0.10196,0.097507,0.094116,0.080214,0.065821]},{"section":13,"text":"In this case, Rattan's fear of having a serious heart disease, even though the doctor says it's nothing, fits into this pattern.","dimension":11,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.05081,0.071272,0.074641,0.077842,0.079134,0.082338,0.087073,0.089259,0.092518,0.097045,0.097514,0.10055],"unified_progress":[0.049343,0.066363,0.072004,0.079046,0.082945,0.088518,0.088978,0.093692,0.092947,0.094463,0.095621,0.096079]},{"section":14,"text":"He's fixated on the idea that the extra heartbeats mean something serious, which is causing him significan